<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>金普新区湾里街道栗苑社区</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>封闭了14天的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>民生园10号楼3单元</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>准时解封</strong></p>
